title: This is the problem with hexakill TT
body:
People get a taste for Kat once more, and then they leave the Twisted-Treeline and start infesting the Rift again.

I have now encountered 2 separate **lvl 7** mastery Katarina's in 2 games. 

That is an oxymoron if ever i saw one. Mastery. Katarina.
